This exhaustive compilation, this *glossary* of geology, is a list of terms and concepts. All of them, I assure you, are relevant to [geology](/Geology), its various subdivisions, and the fields that orbit it. If you’re looking for other terms related to the [Earth sciences](/Earth_sciences), you might find them in the [Glossary of geography terms (disambiguation)](/Glossary_of_geography_terms_(disambiguation)). Don’t expect me to hold your hand.

